casebody.data:
Kathleen D'AGOSTINO, et al., petitioners,
v.
Charlie BAKER, Governor of Massachusetts, et al. No. 15-1347. Supreme Court of the United States June 13, 2016.

Motion of Cato Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit denied.
